{"tid":1912062,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[黃標事件] Google會面的最後一塊拼圖 - 于非 ft. 劉細良","createTime":"2020-03-05T19:47:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-06T06:26:58.000Z","uid":130568,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"476c9b276633a835fde38039b302d879d9b64b9e","tid":1912062,"uid":130568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T19:47:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/F9d6VvaDKDM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FF9d6VvaDKDM&d=%2FrzxgVsCSRBeEmt1flTkcIWZOtE43EI%2FqUWggxD1P9E%3D&h=7167549f\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/F9d6VvaDKDM</a><br />\n摘要<br />\n1. Youtube話黃標係唔會有channel歷史背景審查, 而係一條片一條片獨立判斷<br />\n但依個明顯與事實不符，因為唔少同肺炎冇關嘅片都係自動黃標<br />\n2. 細良佢地嘅片早響1月初開始被黃標 (駱惠寧出任中聯辦主任)<br />\n表示1月30日之前youtube已經有政府審查。再之前台灣好多反送中嘅片都有被黃標。肺炎只係問題嘅表面，冰山嘅一角。<br />\n3. 細良認為：Google作個story出黎去自欺欺人，認為自己只係賺錢，冇奶共<br />\n如果中美貿易戰傾得成，Google可以入中國，Google就會正式出賣畀魔鬼<br />\n4. Youtube既新審查機制係「自我審查」，變相自我壓榨創作空間<br />\n5. Youtube係香港言論自由的最後一條防線<br />\n....<br />\n因為佢地講好雜, 好多細point (例如: WHO響事件既角色、google染紅會點樣危及美國關係法同一國兩制), 有興趣既自己睇, cls<br />\n<br />\n上集提要<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1909968/\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1909968/</a>"},{"pid":"cc11620e4ef05b56c4686140724239b3f4f88f63","tid":1912062,"uid":130568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T19:47:50.000Z","msg":"幫自己賣廣告<br />\n香港Youtube圖書館<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/HKTube_Library\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2FHKTube_Library&d=%2FrzxgVsCSRBeEmt1flTkcIWZOtE43EI%2FqUWggxD1P9E%3D&h=ab3d6a99\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/HKTube_Library</a><br />\nIG影片推介<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/yellowyoutubehk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fyellowyoutubehk%2F&d=%2FrzxgVsCSRBeEmt1flTkcIWZOtE43EI%2FqUWggxD1P9E%3D&h=8af4ce43\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/yellowyoutubehk/</a><br />\nTG每日影片推介<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/hkyoutubelibrary\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkyoutubelibrary&d=%2FrzxgVsCSRBeEmt1flTkcIWZOtE43EI%2FqUWggxD1P9E%3D&h=94e2eac9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hkyoutubelibrary</a>"},{"pid":"4e1bd9ef4745f31020f3c90351444a56f238b229","tid":1912062,"uid":312598,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T23:41:59.000Z","msg":"同美國嘈囉拍片講有咩用"},{"pid":"bb6515238915f0255a8d3985c6598ce3e49ae623","tid":1912062,"uid":130568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T05:19:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"098d359ec224453074b5b52f939e993b5ac31f11","tid":1912062,"uid":12558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T05:22:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c89260e6700eccee61d275461464d050fee0237b","tid":1912062,"uid":130568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T06:26:58.000Z","msg":"推"}]}